OL,6,FAccidental drowning deaths are likely
OL,7,Fto increase during hot weather,
OL,8,Fstudies have found.
OL,10,FTwo independent studies ` one by
OL,11,FBournemouth University and the other
OL,12,Fby the Royal Life Saving Society UK
OL,13,F(RLSS UK) ` both conclude that more
OL,14,Fpeople lose their lives to accidental
OL,15,Fdrowning in the UK during periods of
OL,16,Fhot weather.
