OL,3,CAccidental drowning deaths likely to
OL,4,Cincrease during hot weather, says study
OL,6,FDuring peak temperatures, the findings
OL,7,Falso found that teenagers and young
OL,8,Fadults are proportionately more likely
OL,9,Fto lose their lives.
OL,11,FDawn Whittaker, Chair of the UK
OL,12,FNational Water Safety Forum, explained
OL,13,Fwhy there is an increase in deaths.
OL,15,FShe said: "That increase is really
OL,16,Fbecause more people are attracted to
OL,17,Fwater when it's hot to go and cool off
OL,18,For to enjoy the beach.
